294
00:14:21,100 --> 00:14:21,940
To my surprise,

295
00:14:22,180 --> 00:14:23,300
a miracle came,

296
00:14:23,300 --> 00:14:25,290
and we exchanged our souls.

297
00:14:25,290 --> 00:14:26,420
I became

298
00:14:26,420 --> 00:14:29,010
someone who can stay with him every day.

299
00:14:30,180 --> 00:14:33,180
At first, my feelings for him were just

300
00:14:33,560 --> 00:14:35,990
a beautiful fantasy for youth,

301
00:14:35,990 --> 00:14:38,170
but after spending a few days with him,

302
00:14:38,170 --> 00:14:39,220
I realized

303
00:14:39,600 --> 00:14:40,820
I really like him,

304
00:14:41,140 --> 00:14:46,100
