309
00:15:03,920 --> 00:15:05,990
Then after we switch back,

310
00:15:06,430 --> 00:15:08,050
after I get into college,

311
00:15:08,050 --> 00:15:09,880
can you help me pursue Chen Changning?

312
00:15:12,970 --> 00:15:14,520
