313
00:15:16,060 --> 00:15:16,930
Let's wait until then.

314
00:15:18,640 --> 00:15:19,480
Jing'an...

315
00:15:28,890 --> 00:15:30,410
Do you think

316
00:15:30,640 --> 00:15:32,290
Chen Changning has been

317
00:15:32,290 --> 00:15:33,640
a bit close to the fake Zhu Niannian?

318
00:15:34,010 --> 00:15:35,600
Is it possible that he likes her?

319
00:15:35,600 --> 00:15:36,440
No way.

320
00:15:37,720 --> 00:15:39,680
Niannian is just acting as his sister.

321
00:15:39,680 --> 00:15:40,850
Of course he'd help her.

322
00:15:41,770 --> 00:15:42,670
No.

323
00:15:43,140 --> 00:15:44,220
You're wrong.

324
00:15:45,010 --> 00:15:45,850
Chen Changning

325
00:15:45,850 --> 00:15:47,430
doesn't know you exchanged souls.

326
00:15:47,850 --> 00:15:49,180
Now you're Zhu Niannian.

327
00:15:49,720 --> 00:15:51,300
Chen Jing'an isn't the one

328
00:15:51,300 --> 00:15:52,310
who's being mocked by others.

329
00:15:52,600 --> 00:15:53,600
Do you get it?

330
00:15:54,640 --> 00:15:56,260
The person Chen Changning

331
00:15:56,260 --> 00:15:57,140
is trying to protect

332
00:15:57,470 --> 00:15:58,810
is not you

333
00:15:59,180 --> 00:16:00,520
