to confess my feelings.

374
00:17:52,430 --> 00:17:53,970
Go for it.

375
00:17:53,970 --> 00:17:56,220
I'll try to set you up with him.

376
00:18:04,140 --> 00:18:05,350
Have some hot water.

377
00:18:06,890 --> 00:18:08,100
What for?

378
00:18:09,100 --> 00:18:11,170
I bought something you need.

379
00:18:11,970 --> 00:18:12,850
What?

380
00:18:26,630 --> 00:18:27,720
