392
00:19:04,010 --> 00:19:04,910
And

393
00:19:04,910 --> 00:19:06,760
hundreds of meteors

394
00:19:07,010 --> 00:19:08,220
will streak across the sky.

395
00:19:08,640 --> 00:19:10,430
It's really rare to see

396
00:19:10,430 --> 00:19:11,760
