397
00:19:12,060 --> 00:19:13,010
in such a short time.

398
00:19:13,350 --> 00:19:14,630
Mom, take a break.

399
00:19:14,630 --> 00:19:15,510
Leave it to me.

400
00:19:15,510 --> 00:19:17,640
Stop pretending. I'm done with it.

401
00:19:17,640 --> 00:19:18,750
Go to your room and study.

402
00:19:18,750 --> 00:19:19,890
Mom, just let me help you.

403
00:19:19,890 --> 00:19:21,340
I want to do something for you.

404
00:19:21,340 --> 00:19:23,140
Thank you for cooking for me every day.

405
00:19:24,100 --> 00:19:24,940
Hey,

406
00:19:25,350 --> 00:19:26,760
